Author: temporarymoodswings
Text: OMAD doesn't work for everyone, true. I used to follow a few IF/OMAD YT channels back when I first heard about the whole thing. And they did warn us about not doing it if we have a history with EDs, so I give them that. Too bad I didn't listen.

Author: summerservice
Text: mood... legit no matter how much I eat in a sitting, whether it be 3 crackers or an entire olive garden entree, I WILL be hungry again a few hours later
